{"about_the_game":"Looped is a short interactive story in which you solve mini-puzzles to progress a peaceful story about love, rockets, and time travel.<br><br>This is a story of a love-at-first-sight so powerful it creates a wormhole in time. From the end to the beginning and back again, you follow Him and Her and help them with tasks along their way.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/HoldingHands.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><br>A black hole appears suddenly in a young woman\u2019s living room. An unconscious man falls out. He opens his eyes and it\u2019s love at first sight. Or is this the first sight?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/White_Line_Width616.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/Rocket_Puzzle_616x384.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><br>Features<br>- A wordless story based on an award-winning short film<br>- Illustrated with beautiful hand-drawn 2D frame-by-frame animation<br>- Original soundtrack by United Sound<br>- Find the hidden Easter eggs<br><br><br>\u201cLooped\u201d is based on the award-winning short film of the same name, with the film based on the short story appearing in the book Ouvertyr och andra sagor f\u00f6r n\u00e4stan vuxna written by Thomas Costa Fret\u00e9 in 2022.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/White_Line_Width616.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/EatingCake.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727850/extras/puzzle_ch07_rocketpuzzle.gif?t=1720643077\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.ak